By continuously optimizing our UI/UX design, we ensure that our platforms not only reflect the beauty and tranquility of holistic healing but also provide a seamless and engaging experience for our members. This dedication to improving our virtual interactions directly supports our mission of restoring forgotten healing methodologies, fostering a space where healing over profits, and nature over synthetic solutions, resonate in every design element.


These UI/UX enhancements showcase our solidarity towards providing accessible, joyous, and meaningful digital experiences that underline the values of the Forgotten Formula PMA — nurturing a health-conscious community through intuitive design and user empowerment.


